## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="298cd-104">這個屬性標記的方法會執行 WMI get 作業的基礎結構使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="298cd-104">This attribute marks the method that the infrastructure uses to perform the WMI get operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="298cd-105">此方法必須對應之 WMI 類別的索引鍵值，做為參數並傳回 WMI 類別相關聯的執行個體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="298cd-105">The method must take the key values of the corresponding WMI class as parameters and return the associated instance of the WMI class.</span></span>  
  
 > [!IMPORTANT]
 > <span data-ttu-id="298cd-106">方法參數必須有完全相同的名稱和型別，做為類別的索引鍵參數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="298cd-106">The method parameters must have exactly the same name and type as the key parameters of the class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="298cd-107">所識別的主要參數<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementKeyAttribute>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="298cd-107">The key parameters are identified by the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementKeyAttribute> attribute.</span></span>
  
 <span data-ttu-id="298cd-108">此方法必須將值指派為類別的所有已檢測的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="298cd-108">The method must assign values to all instrumented properties of the class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="298cd-109">當 WMI 提供者擴充基礎結構需要這項繫結功能時，會先搜尋這個屬性的建構函式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="298cd-109">When the WMI Provider Extensions infrastructure requires this binding functionality, it first searches for a constructor with this attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="298cd-110">如果找不到，就會搜尋傳回 WMI 類別類型的靜態方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="298cd-110">If none is found, it then searches for a static method that returns the WMI class type.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="298cd-111">此屬性的目標必須是方法或靜態方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="298cd-111">The target of this attribute must be either a method or a static method.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="298cd-112">下列範例示範如何使用 ManagementBind 屬性來標示類別的建構函式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="298cd-112">The following example shows how to use the ManagementBind attribute to mark the constructor of a class.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Use the ManagementBind attribute to specify that this constructor  
// is used to attach a class instance to a specific WMI  
// instance. The constructor should set the values of the  
// key properties of the WMI instance.  
[ManagementBind]  
public ClassConstructor(int Id)  
{  
     // Set this class instance to a specific instance  
     // by assigning property values and   
     // giving unique values to the key properties.   
}  
```
